{"tid":1634902,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"講就Be Water，但連水嘅特性都唔知。","createTime":"2019-10-07T10:40:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T16:03:11.000Z","uid":281313,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fa8c185926994e42115d93cbf3f2882eef5900bf","tid":1634902,"uid":281313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:41:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無常態</span><br />\n開始有淺黃割，唔好屌佢著，自己都要反思現象。<br />\n我地開頭大受好評，係因為軟硬手法都有。<br />\n林鄭搞緊急法，就係想你嬲，然後只用勇武。<br />\n而且佢似乎成功獲得到民意。<br />\n<br />\n唔係話勇武有咩問題，但要講時機！<br />\n多人話唔中意破壞、強攻，<br />\n咁咪隨著個勢、和理上場囉！<br />\n<strong>勇武可以和理，和理可以勇武</strong><br />\n<strong>咁先係無常態嘅水</strong><br />\n無話割，無話唔再支持勇武，<br />\n但要講<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">時機</span>！<br />\n<br />\n四個月都贏緊，唔好輸一時之憤！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"3fe40e6ee4fc7ca90a5babba1c3fdcb989b6dcec","tid":1634902,"uid":281313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:41:14.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"9b8e8534419158a4a8f5425f043ed79c771b8b98","tid":1634902,"uid":281313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:41:24.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"398b05a1f029a085a14f66b96ea18f457b877197","tid":1634902,"uid":281313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:41:35.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"668f81300b9b191e641ebe46f965b7d584fc5460","tid":1634902,"uid":281313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:42:10.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"bc25177ee3ac085680b03efb74aaccb258583519","tid":1634902,"uid":281313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:42:20.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"c412a85f99b0b8c8320eb45060c187923925d789","tid":1634902,"uid":281313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:42:31.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"fc42e8a6f5bcef2ce9ca112f19da6680e75659c3","tid":1634902,"uid":281313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi